articles.author: Claire Osborn, Tony Plohetski
articles.title: Two people killed, multiple wounded in shooting at Juneteenth celebration in Round Rock - Austin American-Statesman
articles.description: Two people were killed and at least six were injured in a shooting at a Juneteenth celebration at a Round Rock park on Saturday night, police said.
articles.content:
Two people were killed and multiple bystanders were wounded in a shooting at a Juneteenth Celebration in a Round Rock park on Saturday night, police said.
